    <criterion testable="true">`dotnet build src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/` completes with zero errors and zero new warnings vs Phase 1 close baseline.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">`dotnet test tests/unit/Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests/Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests.csproj` completes with zero failures; every Phase 2 BFF task (012, 014, 015, 024, 025, 029) has an associated passing test file in the test project (gaps filled by this task if any are surfaced).</criterion>
